# THE V – Frontend environment (optional)

# Self-hosted API (Express + Prisma). When set, auth and feeds use this backend instead of Supabase auth + direct DB.
# Example: http://localhost:4000
# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:4000
#
# For local dev, `.env.development` defaults VITE_API_URL to http://localhost:4000 (copy or edit as needed).

# Supabase (legacy): project id + anon key live in utils/supabase/info.tsx unless you override here.
# Edge Function "make-server-78efa14d" is used when VITE_API_URL is not set.
